News center
























Company profile
















Shenzhen Textile (Holdings) Co., Ltd ，founded in 1994 on the basis of the state-owned Shenzhen Textile Industry Company, was listed on Shenzhen Stock Exchange in name of “Shen Fangzhi A” and “Shen Fangzhi B”in August 1994.
The Group is mainly engaged in manufacturing , including import and export, of textile, garment and its relevant products, as well as property leasing, warehousing ,real estate development, hotel, and photoelectron materials manufacturing.







