					Full Description



		SHENZHEN TEXTILE (HOLDINGS)CO., LTD. is a China-based company principally engaged in the manufacture and sales of polarizers. The Company is also engaged in the property leasing and apparel trading businesses. The Company's polarizers are mainly used in the manufacture of liquid crystal display panels of smart phones, tablet person computer (PCs), television (TVs), organic light emitting diode (OLED) display panels, as well as the filter lens of instruments, sunglasses and photographic equipment. The Company mainly distributes its products in domestic and overseas markets.
