Sunday, 11 Jun 2017 11:06pm EDT 
June 12(Reuters) - Shenzhen Textile Holdings Co Ltd <000045.SZ> ::* Says its unit signed a cooperation agreement with Kunshan-based photoelectric material company for LGP production line project.* Says its unit signed a cooperation agreement with Zhejiang-based photoelectric material company for liquid crystal reflective film production line project. 
			
