Shenzhen Textile (Holdings) Co Ltd:Sees net loss for 2016 Q1 to be 8 mln yuan to 12 mln yuan.Says the net profit of 2015 Q1 was 4.34 mln yuan.Comments that income from selling financial assets is the main reason for the forecast. 
			
