Summary for Shenzhen Textile (Holdings) Co.,Ltd.
Shenzhen Textile (Holdings) Co., Ltd. is primarily engaged in the manufacture and sale of textile apparels, polarizers and related products, as well as property leasing business. The Company operates its businesses through industrial products, which provides polarizers for liquid crystal displays (LCDs) and apparels; property leasing and management, which include hotels operation and the leasing services of commercial shops, factories, office buildings and warehouses, among others, as well as trading business.


